item.title: Zezima?
item.dc:creator: @davidude36 Brolapse
item.description:
@davidude36 wrote:

`Rich:

Well, he does have no pure, we all already know, and whoever says they know they know hes pure, are complete dumbass’s.

Well we cannot be sure of this can we? None of us are Zezima, so we cannot tell what he does. He could have a level 3 account and run around going “free stoof please” and so we could never know he owned the account. And then we also have noob imposters whom run around saying “My other account is zezima” so then some people start to think that he does have another account.

Also anyone posting in this thread saying “OMG SHUT UP ITS JUST A GUY AND HE IS NOTHING SPECIAL” well think about it, you could say the same about Britany Spears or The Queen of England (In b4 pom). But they all are famous for one or another reasons, and are famous in different ways. The queen is famous for being a monarchy(Sp?), Britany Spears is famous for being a pop star, among other things and being the best at being a popstar too and finally Zezima is famous to Runescape players because he managed to be the best at the game, and get a score which is impossible in some peoples eyes.

Therefore in conclusion; Stfu people posting shit like “OMG STFU ABOUT ZEZIMA”.
